==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cariole
<hw>Car"i*ole</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>carriole</ets>, dim. fr. L. <ets>carrus</ets>. See <er>Car</er>,
and <er>Carryall</er>.]</ety> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A small, light, open
one-horse carriage</def>. <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A covered cart</def>.
<sd>(c)</sd> <def>A kind of calash. See <er>Carryall</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cariopsis</ent>⟦br⟧
